tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits except for a low HbA1c (3.3%), which may indicate recent hypoglycemia, anemia, or altered red cell turnover. Glucose is normal. Renal function and electrolytes are unremarkable. Correlate clinically for possible causes of low HbA1c and consider further evaluation if indicated.
